title: 51. America ... F*ck Yeah! - Part 1
itunes:title: 51. America ... F*ck Yeah! - Part 1
description: While you’re poppin’ open bottles of Miller Lite and lighting up Roman candles for the 4th, listen as the crew takes aim at the tyrannical threats to the future of our democracy; namely, the two worthless political parties, the woke mob, and the Media That Cried Wolf. You won’t want to miss Andy’s essential tips for reclaiming American greatness, or his shocking prediction about events to come. He hopes he’s not right, but...when has he ever been wrong?
